name: respect the budget - women
description:
to GET what we want...
we have to respect the budget

our desires and needs can be had...if we plan for them. put simply, budgeting is planning our income (salary, profits, dividend payments) and expenses (savings, rent, food, transportation, credit card bills, etc.) this shirt is all about spending within our means.

black shirt. red and white print.

american apparel
100% fine jersey cotton construction. durable rib neckband. form-fitting. made in the u.s.a.

name: it all adds up - women
description:
Over the course of a year…

one $3 lotto ticket per week = $156

a $25 order of pizza & wings each month = $300

“weekdays only” caffeine fix at $2.50 a pop = $600

some expenses don’t seem like much, but they do add up! one…penny…at…a…time.

get creative and explore ways to save your ‘moolah’. clip coupons... prepare food at home...shop on sale... buy only what you need... the opportunities are endless.

white shirt. gray and black print.

american apparel
100% fine jersey cotton construction. durable rib neckband. form-fitting. made in the u.s.a.
